{"tid":1394514,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港隊北上比賽遭深圳隊員圍毆 港冰球協會：感謝中方迅速認真處理","createTime":"2019-08-01T12:22:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T16:04:12.000Z","uid":133680,"like":4,"dislike":328,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"df4cc569665000d9ecd192be48f5699a98ac9480","tid":1394514,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T12:22:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/420361564693683/posts/2503100326419786/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F420361564693683%2Fposts%2F2503100326419786%2F&d=BmTzKXBjX6ru83xd6aIIEQESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=2ed97c9a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/420361564693683/posts/2503100326419786/</a><br />\n<br />\n【北上比賽遭深圳隊員圍毆 港冰球協會：感謝中方迅速認真處理】<br />\n<br />\n今日（8月1日）網上流傳片段，指香港冰球代表隊於第二屆全國青運會比賽期間，被深圳的隊員毆打。<br />\n<br />\n事發於昨日，港隊與「崑崙鴻星萬科龍隊」的U20比賽中，港隊領先11:2，負方懷疑惱羞成怒，7名隊員圍毆5名港隊成員。<br />\n<br />\n香港冰球協會於官方專頁交代事件，承認昨日確實有不愉快事件發生。聲明指經過中國冰球協會積極認真處理，事件已經得到解決。聲明引述中國冰球協會取消了深圳隊的3名犯規球員一年參加冰球比賽的資格，更保證以後不會有這些事情會再發生。<br />\n<br />\n香港冰球協會感謝中國冰球協會的迅速認真處理方法，又稱對以後兩地冰球發展和交流充滿信心。<br />\n<br />\n全文︰<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/08-01-2019/54791\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F08-01-2019%2F54791&d=BmTzKXBjX6ru83xd6aIIEQESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=3be200a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/08-01-2019/54791</a><br />\n<br />\n#冰球<br />\n<br />\n請支持PassionPrime：<br />\n<a href=\"http://passiontimes.hk/prime/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpassiontimes.hk%2Fprime%2F&d=BmTzKXBjX6ru83xd6aIIEQESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=2516df5c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://passiontimes.hk/prime/</a><br />\n<br />\n請支持熱血時報印刷版︰<br />\n<a href=\"http://passiontimes.hk/4.0/regform.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpassiontimes.hk%2F4.0%2Fregform.php&d=BmTzKXBjX6ru83xd6aIIEQESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=07dd6e55\" d